    "Biomedical subdomain-specific models, similar to MentalLlaMA for the subdomain of mental health, are also envisaged.LLMs have brought about a new paradigm in biomedical NLP research and application, enabling us to make substantial progress on problems that appeared unsolvable even in the recent past (e.g., QA).",
